-- Speedy Hire Gets $50 Million Gulf Oil Deal, Mail on Sunday Says
-- B y   S t e p h e n   M o r r i s
-- 2012-07-29T11:45:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-29/speedy-hire-gets-50-million-gulf-oil-deal-mail-on-sunday-says.html
Speedy Hire Plc (SDY) , a U.K. construction
equipment-leasing company, won a 32 million-pound ($50 million)
order from Abu Dhabi National Oil Co., the Mail on Sunday
reported, citing a company announcement.  The company will provide and manage equipment for Abu
Dhabi’s Upper Zakum oil field, the world’s fourth largest, the
newspaper said. Speedy Hire is attempting to boost its sales
outside the U.K. to 10 percent from 3 percent currently,
according to the article.  To contact the reporter on this story:
